Description: Describes the advantage of having a good "regeneration speed" value. Essentially this means that when the subject's own health is regenerating, it will go faster than usual.

French.Translation: Le sujet régénère sa santé plus rapidement.

Italian.Translation: La salute del soggetto migliorerà più rapidamente.

Spanish.Translation: El sujeto recuperará salud más rápido.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: O indivíduo regenera saúde mais rápido.

Japanese.Translation: 対象の体力リジェネが早くなる。

Chinese_Traditional.Translation: 實驗對象生命值恢復速度較快。

Chinese_Simplified.Translation: 使用者的生命值恢复速度加快。

name: BoosterImplants.Effects.RegenerationSpeedDescription
